ho have lost their appetite."},{"version":"firered","text":"It lays several eggs a day. The eggs are apparently rich in nutrients and extremely delicious."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"A rare and elusive POK\u00e9MON that is said to bring happiness to those who manage to catch one."},{"version":"diamond","text":"It is said to deliver happiness. Being compassionate, it shares its eggs with injured people."},{"version":"pearl","text":"It lays several eggs a day and won\u2019t share them with those who have evil in their hearts."},{"version":"platinum","text":"A kindly Pok\u00e9mon that lays highly nutritious eggs and shares them with injured Pok\u00e9mon or people."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"It walks carefully to prevent its egg from breaking. However, it is extremely fast at running away."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"Being few in number and difficult to capture, it is said to bring happiness to the Trainer who catches it."},{"version":"black","text":"A kindly Pok\u00e9mon that lays highly nutritious eggs and shares them with injured Pok\u00e9mon or people."},{"version":"white","text":"A kindly Pok\u00e9mon that lays highly nutritious eggs and shares them with injured Pok\u00e9mon or people."},{"version":"black-2","text":"A kindly Pok\u00e9mon that lays highly nutritious eggs and shares them with injured Pok\u00e9mon or people."},{"version":"white-2","text":"A kindly Pok\u00e9mon that lays highly nutritious eggs and shares them with injured Pok\u00e9mon or people."},{"version":"x","text":"It is said to deliver happiness. Being compassionate, it shares its eggs with injured people."},{"version":"y","text":"It lays several eggs a day. The eggs are apparently rich in nutrients and extremely delicious."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Chansey lays nutritionally excellent eggs on an everyday basis. The eggs are so delicious, they are easily and eagerly devoured by even those people who have lost their appetite."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Chansey lays nutritionally excellent eggs on an everyday basis. The eggs are so delicious, they are easily and eagerly devoured by even those people who have lost their appetite."},{"version":"sun","text":"The eggs laid by Chansey are rich in nutrients and a favorite food of many Pok\u00e9mon."},{"version":"moon","text":"Not only are these Pok\u00e9mon fast runners, they\u2019re also few in number, so anyone who finds one must be lucky indeed."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"It seems that other Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s efforts to take its delicious, nutritious egg away from it caused Chansey to get faster at fleeing."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"Because the eggs on their bellies have been overharvested by people in the past, the Chansey population remains very small."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"A gentle and kindhearted Pok\u00e9mon that shares its nutritious eggs if it sees an injured Pok\u00e9mon."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"A gentle and kindhearted Pok\u00e9mon that shares its nutritious eggs if it sees an injured Pok\u00e9mon."},{"version":"sword","text":"The egg Chansey carries is not only delicious but also packed with nutrition. It\u2019s used as a high-class cooking ingredient."},{"version":"shield","text":"This species was once very slow. To protect their eggs from other creatures, these Pok\u00e9mon became able to flee quickly."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"This purehearted Pok\u00e9mon shares its eggs with the injured."}],"evo":{"name":"happiny","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"chansey","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":"oval-stone","known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"need